<br>
I actually died, got rez, was totally oom (had 3 normal rods on ground tho).  Used the 3 normal rods to get enough mana for a t-rod.  Cleric hits me with a nice HP buff, and starts celestial elixirs on me (I think that's what it was anyway).  It took me less than 90 seconds to go back up to full mana using t-rods.  My current mana pool is around 3070.  Was very impressed with the mana regen rate I achieved with it.  Note, this didn't include dropping any additional rods to replace the cleric's mana, he had KEI, and was logging out, so he didn't care about losing a bit of mana to heal me while I rodded.<br>
